@bared.monkey has the best price and service in the city for laser. ✨
In the video I’m doing a Picoway Session for a dark spot I got after getting burned by an iron on a modeling job. After one session it is much lighter. 3 to 6 sessions is recommended. Results vary from person to person but this laser is gentle and good for all skin types. 

This is the before the first of 3 series post that I will show the treatments.
